Qwey esth'Nragard, 52nd Level Enchanter, Solusek Ro, Fate's Union<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udulsin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dulsin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/6/02 9:58:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Killing a cleric...</span><hr size=1> My appolgies. I should have clarified what I ment better.<br>
